Design and Layout (20 points)
Consistent and attractive visual design
User-friendly layout and navigation
Mobile responsiveness

Content (30 points)
Relevant, accurate, and up-to-date information
Well-written and properly formatted text
Appropriate use of multimedia (e.g. images, videos)

Functionality (30 points)
Fast loading speed
No broken links or error messages
User-friendly features (e.g. search bar, contact form)

User Experience (20 points)
Easy to use and understand
Intuitive navigation and organization
Engages and informs the user


Total: 100 points
